Interface PartialComponent.Generator<T,C extends PartialComponent<T,C>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - value type of the input image.
    C - component type.
    Enclosing interface:
    PartialComponent<T,C extends PartialComponent<T,C>>

    public static interface PartialComponent.Generator<T,C extends PartialComponent<T,C>>
    Create new components.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      C createComponent(T value)
      Create a new empty component with the given value (e.g., grey-level).
      C createMaxComponent()
      Create a component with a value (e.g., grey-level) greater than any occurring in the input for the BuildComponentTree.
